<Author>GmaJody
<Content>Great Find Was in Phoenix on business and this hotel was close to the office I was working at. Decided to give it a try and am so glad I did. Hotel was clean and comfortable and the staff was very friendly and helpful. Breakfast was your average free breakfast with nice selection of pastries, waffels, and cold cereal. There is a small pool with a very nice patio area to relax.It is a little difficult to get to (it's on a frontage road next to the freeway) but once you figuare it out it is a great location. Plenty of food choices nearby with shopping and entertainment also available. This was my second stay at a Country Suites and have been happy both times. 
