<Author>A TripAdvisor Member
<Content>Feels Like Home There voice mail messages states the Fabulous Country Inn  Suites and they weren't kidding. Wow, what a pleasant surprise. My company suggested this hotel and I can not say how business friendly this hotel is. They serve a very nice breakfast with quite a variety from Belgian waffles, sausage and eggs to bagels, yogurt and fresh fruit. I was able to enjoy my breakfast while checking my e-mail in their breakfast area, with their wireless high speed internet. I utilized the business center to print out my boarding pass which made it nice to get that out of the way. How nice that was! This has to be the cleanest hotel I have ever stayed at. The rooms and the pillow top beds are so comfortable. One last thing, the employees at the hotel made me feel like I was at home. Offering fresh baked cookies to me each day when I would return from work, just like I have at home! 
