<Content>Wonderful accommodations, no transportation worries. All services promised on the phone or listed on the internet were absolutely accurate. Very hospitable staff willing to assure all comforts of guests. Pleasant and comfortable rooms. Inviting fireplace in lobby. Pool and exercise room open 24 hours. Substantial breakfast included in reasonable room rate. Free shuttle to and from airport and the ski equipment rental site. Shuttle service provided to all ski areas or to the ski buses at very reasonable rates. No worry about having to do own driving on mountain roads. If desired however, rental car can be arranged at motel. Personable and considerate staff and manager. You will want to return for subsequent visits. 
